WEBVTT

01:32.467 --> 01:34.034
Jeremy is leaving!

01:34.036 --> 01:36.505
- Hey, bud.
- Jeremy is leaving!

01:39.075 --> 01:42.009
Hey, not my head... phones, Josh.

01:42.011 --> 01:43.643
Jeremy is leaving!

01:43.645 --> 01:45.478
- What's with him today?
- I don't know.

01:45.480 --> 01:46.481
Have you seen my shoes?

01:47.683 --> 01:49.018
- He has my shoes?
- Yes.

01:49.852 --> 01:50.953
Josh!

02:09.972 --> 02:12.405
- Josh!
- Jeremy is leaving!

02:12.407 --> 02:13.606
We know. Stop!

02:13.608 --> 02:15.109
Jared, stop chasing
your brother!

02:15.111 --> 02:16.877
- Give me my shoes.
- Jeremy is leaving!

02:16.879 --> 02:19.680
Tom. Do something!

02:19.682 --> 02:20.981
Jared, stop chasing
your brother.

02:20.983 --> 02:22.049
Jeremy is leaving.

02:22.051 --> 02:24.018
That... That's it? Really?

02:24.020 --> 02:26.153
- Jeremy is leaving.
- We know. Stop.

02:26.155 --> 02:28.090
Come on, dude.
Give me a minute.

02:29.424 --> 02:31.391
Sit down, buddy.

02:31.393 --> 02:32.793
Give me the shoes.

02:32.795 --> 02:33.863
Here's your shoes.

02:35.798 --> 02:37.497
Listen.

02:37.499 --> 02:40.167
I know, I'm leaving,

02:40.169 --> 02:41.769
and you're upset and you
don't know what to do.

02:41.771 --> 02:42.805
So just take
a deep breath, okay?

02:44.606 --> 02:46.341
Jeremy is leaving.

02:47.076 --> 02:48.742
I know.

02:48.744 --> 02:50.545
Here. Listen to this.

02:51.580 --> 02:52.980
This is gonna
cheer you up.

02:54.750 --> 02:56.616
Just like the show, right?

02:56.618 --> 02:57.787
Watch this.

02:59.121 --> 03:00.587
"Kirk to <i>Enterprise."</i>

03:00.589 --> 03:01.889
You try it.

03:01.891 --> 03:04.024
"Kirk to <i>Enterprise.</i>
Hello?"

03:04.026 --> 03:05.558
Listen,
I'm leaving for a while,

03:05.560 --> 03:07.194
but I want you
to have this, okay?

03:07.196 --> 03:09.930
And I promise you
I'm right on the other side.

03:09.932 --> 03:11.198
But that's your phone.

03:11.200 --> 03:13.934
I'll get another one.
New life, new phone.

03:13.936 --> 03:15.637
- Sweet.
- It's yours, buddy.

03:16.504 --> 03:18.005
I love you, okay?

03:18.007 --> 03:19.106
Okay, come on.

03:19.108 --> 03:20.540
Here we go. Let's do it.

03:20.542 --> 03:22.743
- Let's go.
- Come on.

03:22.745 --> 03:24.479
- Thanks, Dad.
- You got it.

03:26.082 --> 03:27.482
- Jeremy.
- Yeah?

03:31.553 --> 03:33.555
Are you sure you don't
wanna take the old guitar?

03:35.157 --> 03:36.458
Dad, it's yours.

03:37.093 --> 03:38.025
Yeah, I know,

03:38.027 --> 03:40.694
but you play it ten
times more than I do.

03:40.696 --> 03:42.029
Dad, I'm not
taking your guitar.

03:42.031 --> 03:43.498
That's your story.

03:47.937 --> 03:49.638
Let's get you to college.

03:59.081 --> 04:00.147
<i>I love you, Mom.</i>

04:00.149 --> 04:01.650
I love you, son.

04:02.685 --> 04:04.118
Be good.

04:04.120 --> 04:05.185
Okay, son.

04:05.187 --> 04:07.821
- Love you, Dad.
- Love you.

04:07.823 --> 04:08.923
See you soon.

04:08.925 --> 04:10.124
Hey. Love you guys.

04:10.126 --> 04:11.827
- Bye.
- Bye-bye. Love you.

04:13.229 --> 04:14.496
Jeremy.

04:16.531 --> 04:17.532
Come here.

04:25.540 --> 04:27.642
No way.

04:29.544 --> 04:30.878
It's a gift
from all of us.

04:30.880 --> 04:32.214
How did you afford this?

04:33.683 --> 04:34.848
They took out a loan.

04:34.850 --> 04:37.051
And we all agreed to no
Christmas gifts this year.

04:37.053 --> 04:38.518
We worked it out.

04:38.520 --> 04:40.553
- Sure.
- Yeah.

04:40.555 --> 04:42.890
You gotta go.

04:42.892 --> 04:45.094
For me,
music is a hobby.

04:45.695 --> 04:46.929
For you,

04:48.731 --> 04:49.799
it's a gift.

04:51.867 --> 04:53.568
So, go write your story.

04:55.705 --> 04:56.770
Go on.

04:56.772 --> 04:58.038
Hurry up.

05:03.846 --> 05:06.048
What would you have done
if he took your old guitar?

05:08.884 --> 05:10.851
Well, I...

05:10.853 --> 05:12.953
I would've kept that one.

06:48.751 --> 06:49.919
Thank you so much.

06:55.291 --> 06:57.026
Thanks. Thank you.

07:11.173 --> 07:13.006
Welcome
to Calvary Chapel College.

07:13.008 --> 07:14.241
Not a bad front yard, huh?

07:14.243 --> 07:15.978
Not bad at all.

07:27.923 --> 07:29.091
