- What's up?

07:37.900 --> 07:39.068
Wait up!

07:55.217 --> 07:56.250
Hold up.

07:56.252 --> 07:57.851
Hey, man.
Uh, Norm sent me to help load in.

07:57.853 --> 07:59.019
- Norm did?
- Yeah.

07:59.021 --> 08:00.723
Okay.
Wait, who's Norm?

08:21.944 --> 08:23.345
Hey, man.
You're Jean-Luc, right?

08:24.280 --> 08:26.914
Yeah. Are you in the crew?

08:26.916 --> 08:29.049
