08:33.155 --> 08:35.155
Uh, cool.

08:35.157 --> 08:36.190
Dude, I love your music.

08:36.192 --> 08:37.958
You're, like, the reason
I came to school here.

08:37.960 --> 08:40.894
- You're a legend.
- Oh, don't know about that.

08:40.896 --> 08:43.263
Uh, anyway,
I was wondering, if, uh,

08:43.265 --> 08:46.300
