sometime about music?

08:46.302 --> 08:48.037
The industry,
how to make it?

08:49.471 --> 08:50.472
"Make it?"

08:51.273 --> 08:52.274
Yeah.

08:53.876 --> 08:54.942
You're asking
the wrong question.

08:54.944 --> 08:56.877
It's not about making it.

08:56.879 --> 09:00.316
It's about whatever our
songs give people. You know?

09:01.450 --> 09:02.885
So, what do you wanna
give people?

09:04.420 --> 09:06.155
- Figure that out first.
- Yeah.

09:07.489 --> 09:09.158
Nice to meet you, man.

09:13.262 --> 09:14.328
Hey.

09:14.330 --> 09:15.831
Yes? Yes?

09:17.533 --> 09:19.235
