09:55.471 --> 10:00.042
<i>♪ Take My hand and walk</i>

10:01.176 --> 10:03.545
<i>♪ Take My hand and walk</i>

10:06.548 --> 10:12.254
<i>♪ Take My hand and walk</i>

10:16.292 --> 10:18.358
That was so good. Love it.

10:18.360 --> 10:20.229
Hey, kid. Guitar!

10:23.932 --> 10:24.998
