- Thanks, man.

10:45.421 --> 10:47.287
Excuse me.
I'm so sorry.

10:56.298 --> 10:57.299
- Hi.
- Hi.

10:59.068 --> 11:00.302
I, um...

11:01.370 --> 11:02.538
I'm Jeremy.

11:03.339 --> 11:04.373
Melissa.

11:05.207 --> 11:06.373
"Melissa."

11:06.375 --> 11:07.576
Yep.

11:08.444 --> 11:10.110
I saw you tonight.

11:10.112 --> 11:12.446
I mean, I was watching you.
"Watching?"

11:13.515 --> 11:15.050
Watched you.

11:16.185 --> 11:17.319
You were watching me?

11:19.321 --> 11:20.422
Okay.

11:21.523 --> 11:23.256
- Okay.
- Melissa.

11:23.258 --> 11:24.259
I gotta go.

11:25.194 --> 11:26.259
Bye.

11:26.261 --> 11:28.328
- Well, I sing too.
- Hmm?

11:28.330 --> 11:30.499
I sing.
I saw you singing.

11:31.367 --> 11:32.368
Nice.

11:34.937 --> 11:35.938
Bye.

11:44.313 --> 11:45.379
<i>A record deal</i>

11:45.381 --> 11:47.114
two years after
you graduated here.

11:47.116 --> 11:49.182
How?

11:49.184 --> 11:51.218
