writing songs, man.

11:51.220 --> 11:52.285
It's all about
the songs.

11:52.287 --> 11:55.455
Write what you care about,
what you're afraid of.

11:55.457 --> 11:58.959
Whatever it is,
it needs to be truth.

11:58.961 --> 12:00.562
