The truth?

12:02.030 --> 12:04.633
Brother, I write
love songs, to God.

12:06.001 --> 12:07.702
Mostly to God.

12:07.704 --> 12:09.369
Sometimes to a girl.

12:09.371 --> 12:10.705
I'm writing one
right now for a girl,

12:10.707 --> 12:12.641
and this girl, man,
she is...

12:14.443 --> 12:17.077
So, yeah.

12:17.079 --> 12:19.513
Write what you love, yeah?
Get after it.

12:19.515 --> 12:21.415
Hasten the day.

12:21.417 --> 12:22.518
What does that mean?

12:24.186 --> 12:26.286
You know, a day
with no more pain,

12:26.288 --> 12:29.358
no suffering,
every tear wiped away.

12:32.394 --> 12:35.228
