pulls that closer.

12:35.230 --> 12:36.298
So...

12:37.633 --> 12:39.001
Hasten the day.

12:48.343 --> 12:51.613
<i>♪ Why it has to hurt so much</i>

12:54.450 --> 12:57.953
<i>♪ Give Me
all your sadness ♪</i>

13:00.690 --> 13:02.692
So, you actually do sing.

13:04.326 --> 13:05.392
And?

13:05.394 --> 13:06.493
And...

13:06.495 --> 13:10.999
I have pretty high standards
when it comes to music,

13:12.100 --> 13:13.368
but it's good.

13:15.070 --> 13:16.436
