13:20.108 --> 13:22.044
Yeah, pretty good.

13:23.178 --> 13:24.179
Do you write
your own songs?

13:25.080 --> 13:26.546
I'm working
on some stuff.

13:26.548 --> 13:27.715
Can I hear it?

13:27.717 --> 13:29.349
- Can you hear it?
- Yeah.

13:29.351 --> 13:31.151
