your journal.

13:31.153 --> 13:33.055
What? No.

13:35.090 --> 13:37.226
- I should get to class.
- Yeah.

13:38.060 --> 13:40.193
You keep singing, Jeremy.

13:40.195 --> 13:42.095
- Camp.
- Hmm?

13:42.097 --> 13:45.499
