13:55.410 --> 13:59.546
Oh, okay. Well, if you
find yourself free at 8:00,

13:59.548 --> 14:01.481
I'll be at the beach,
Oceanside Pier.

14:01.483 --> 14:04.084
You know, stop on by.

14:04.086 --> 14:05.151
