literally just asked me out

14:10.793 --> 14:12.492
just right over here.

14:12.494 --> 14:13.730
We'll see.

14:16.098 --> 14:19.232
Oh, yeah, and you should, um,
bring your guitar as well.

14:19.234 --> 14:20.701
Okay.

14:20.703 --> 14:22.737
- It's a date.
- Not a date!

14:22.739 --> 14:23.806
Not.

14:25.541 --> 14:26.709
It's a date.

14:29.511 --> 14:30.680
