I didn't know you guys were friends.

15:00.142 --> 15:01.608
Oh, yeah.
He's my best friend.

15:01.610 --> 15:03.778
No, you just
keep taking my food.

15:03.780 --> 15:06.613
Well, why won't
you share these?

15:06.615 --> 15:08.648
