uh, been friends for?

15:08.650 --> 15:10.350
Oh, um...

15:10.352 --> 15:13.253
Like, freshman year.
I was working at Sunset Point.

15:13.255 --> 15:14.454
Right,
at the restaurant.

15:14.456 --> 15:15.756
- Mmm-hmm.
- And then we kind of started

15:15.758 --> 15:17.692
this, uh, tradition,
I guess, here.

15:17.694 --> 15:19.292
Mmm-hmm.
Oh, actually, though,

15:19.294 --> 15:21.394
you were truly
my running partner

15:21.396 --> 15:23.496
- for my first year at school.
