to become a rock star

15:25.167 --> 15:26.333
and get lazy on me.

15:26.335 --> 15:27.603
Yeah. Here we are.

15:31.440 --> 15:33.206
You brought your guitar.

15:33.208 --> 15:35.342
I did. Well,
you asked me to.

15:35.344 --> 15:36.877
Right, right. I did.

15:36.879 --> 15:40.347
Maybe you should, um,
start us off with a song.

15:40.349 --> 15:41.949
