Do you have a song that you like?

15:54.931 --> 15:57.631
All right.
I guess I'm playing a song.

15:59.702 --> 16:01.201
Uh, <i>Find Me In The River?</i>

16:01.203 --> 16:03.171
Yeah. I love that song.

16:03.873 --> 16:04.874
All right.

